        <p>
            Each data point in a series can be represented by a symbol as a marker. You can customize the shape, size, and color of the symbol with the <a target="_blank" href="https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-js2/Syncfusion.EJ2.Charts.ChartMarkerSettingsBuilder.html#methods">ChartMarker</a> class.
        </p>
        <p>
            <code>Tooltip</code> is enabled in this example. To see the tooltip in action, hover over a point or tap on a point in touch-enabled devices.
        </p>
        <p>
            More information about the marker can be found in this
            <a target="_blank" href="https://ej2.syncfusion.com/aspnetcore/documentation/chart/data-markers">documentation section</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
}
